1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,260 --> 00:01:45,780
=Episode 28=

16
00:01:50,159 --> 00:01:52,239
If Rao Yuci leaves Lysen,

17
00:01:52,799 --> 00:01:53,879
is there anyone

18
00:01:54,079 --> 00:01:55,239
in Dept 3 more suited

19
00:01:55,239 --> 00:01:56,959
to lead this team than you?

20
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,959
If you handle this well,

21
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:04,040
Mr. Jiang

22
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,680
will treat you well.

23
00:02:54,700 --> 00:02:55,879
You should go get checked out too.

24
00:02:55,879 --> 00:02:56,680
You're crazy.

25
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:57,879
Go take your meds.

26
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:13,759
Ms. Rao.

27
00:03:15,580 --> 00:03:16,719
The coffee machine is broken.

28
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,879
I told Admin,

29
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:21,919
but they haven't fixed it yet.

30
00:03:27,039 --> 00:03:27,840
Ms. Rao.

31
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,319
I'm just heading down for coffee.

32
00:03:32,319 --> 00:03:33,120
Can I get you one?

33
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,599
Thanks.

34
00:03:46,100 --> 00:03:48,060
(Jiang Dongchao)

35
00:03:54,199 --> 00:03:55,000
Sima,

36
00:03:55,639 --> 00:03:57,159
where in Jiangxi are you from?

37
00:03:58,039 --> 00:03:59,159
Nanchang, Mr. Jiang.

38
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:01,240
I'm from Shangrao.
We're practically neighbors.

39
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,120
It hasn't been easy for you.

40
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,280
No connections, no backing,

41
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,919
you've fought for everything
on your own.

42
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,479
Look,

43
00:04:10,719 --> 00:04:11,879
in all of Investment Dept 3,

44
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,690
you're the only one left standing.

45
00:04:14,879 --> 00:04:16,639
That proves you're a real fighter.

46
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:19,360
Thank you, Mr. Jiang.

47
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:22,759
Last night,

48
00:04:22,959 --> 00:04:24,399
Ms. Bai was telling me about you.

49
00:04:25,759 --> 00:04:26,839
She said Sima Yang

50
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,720
has a lot of potential.

51
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:31,839
But I think

52
00:04:31,839 --> 00:04:32,839
you're still missing

53
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,120
one final edge.

54
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,279
Here,

55
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:42,879
help me with the blinds.

56
00:04:42,879 --> 00:04:43,600
You got it.

57
00:05:09,079 --> 00:05:10,439
You've been at Lysen for years.

58
00:05:12,319 --> 00:05:13,920
I should have brought you up here sooner

59
00:05:14,079 --> 00:05:15,399
to see this view.

60
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,360
How high

61
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,279
a person can climb

62
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:22,480
usually depends

63
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:23,639
on the choices they make.

64
00:05:24,439 --> 00:05:25,639
When making a choice,

65
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,680
if you can't see

66
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:30,079
what's truly in your best interest,
where it lies,

67
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,439
you'll never reach

68
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,920
the top floor of life

69
00:05:34,279 --> 00:05:35,399
to look down on the world.

70
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:39,879
To do great things...

71
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:48,920
You have to burn your bridges.

72
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,879
Sir, your coffee is ready.

73
00:06:12,879 --> 00:06:13,480
Thanks.

74
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,199
No problem.

75
00:06:18,439 --> 00:06:19,000
Sir,

76
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,360
your to-go coffee is ready.

77
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,160
Sir?

78
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,160
Sir?

79
00:06:22,399 --> 00:06:23,680
Your coffee is ready.

80
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:24,439
Oh, thanks.

81
00:06:32,279 --> 00:06:33,079
Come in.

82
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:35,759
Thanks.

83
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,279
No problem.

84
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,600
The sky looks ominous.

85
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,079
Something big is going down

86
00:07:15,519 --> 00:07:17,279
at Lysen Group tonight.

87
00:07:53,820 --> 00:07:56,660
(Chen Mo)

88
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:59,560
(One day ago)
This is the file on Chen Mo.

89
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,600
I'm sure you'll find it interesting.

90
00:08:17,319 --> 00:08:18,240
If I give this

91
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,480
to Rao Yuci,

92
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:22,040
how do you think she'll react?

93
00:08:28,319 --> 00:08:30,040
For everything Rao Yuci did to me,

94
00:08:30,879 --> 00:08:33,320
I'll make her pay a hundredfold.

95
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,519
When I want something done,

96
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:38,200
no one can stop me.

97
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,080
I want her to rot in hell.

98
00:08:42,879 --> 00:08:44,840
She's been there before.

99
00:08:45,799 --> 00:08:47,279
But this time,

100
00:08:48,679 --> 00:08:50,399
I'm never letting her out.

101
00:09:00,679 --> 00:09:02,320
Your girlfriend's lost it.

102
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,519
She's at Lysen Group.

103
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,879
Get over here and see her.

104
00:10:09,159 --> 00:10:10,440
Look at you.

105
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:13,639
You're in even worse shape
than you were three years ago.

106
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,879
And I love it.

107
00:10:22,639 --> 00:10:23,480
Fragile.

108
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,279
Helpless.

109
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,360
Broken.

110
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:34,559
You managed to get out

111
00:10:34,559 --> 00:10:35,820
after I sent you away last time.

112
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:37,720
But this time,

113
00:10:38,559 --> 00:10:40,120
you won't be as lucky.

114
00:10:41,399 --> 00:10:44,080
You're never getting out of here again.

115
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,120
My dear.

116
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:50,360
Your end is nigh.

117
00:11:02,660 --> 00:11:04,200
I'm afraid I'm going to disappoint you.

118
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,120
Ms. Rao.

119
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:10,039
I've already called the police.

120
00:11:23,759 --> 00:11:25,279
Let me introduce you to someone.

121
00:11:26,039 --> 00:11:28,159
(One year ago)
He's a student I've been sponsoring.

122
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:30,039
He's at Lysen Group now.

123
00:11:30,279 --> 00:11:31,679
At Lysen Group, you need

124
00:11:31,679 --> 00:11:33,240
an ally who looks like an enemy.

125
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:36,120
He'll always be against you,

126
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:38,000
but he'll help you.

127
00:11:38,559 --> 00:11:39,639
You have to trust him.

128
00:11:41,879 --> 00:11:43,960
Hello. I'm Sima Yang.

129
00:11:56,279 --> 00:11:57,799
I found this on her computer.

130
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,440
It's being delivered tomorrow.

131
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:01,720
How do you know

132
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:03,240
she isn't just using it for fruit?

133
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,240
A fruit knife?

134
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:08,000
Why would she keep staring at it?

135
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,279
Besides,

136
00:12:09,279 --> 00:12:11,279
Rao Yuci and Manager Yu's
recent conversations

137
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:13,039
have been all about you.

138
00:12:16,399 --> 00:12:17,759
Be careful, Ms. Bai.

139
00:12:29,799 --> 00:12:31,120
She already has the photos.

140
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:35,399
Dept 3 should have finished

141
00:12:35,399 --> 00:12:37,080
the project proposal long ago.

142
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:37,879
Send it to me.

143
00:12:38,159 --> 00:12:39,720
I haven't had the chance.

144
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:41,840
Only Manager Yu,

145
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:42,480
Rao Yuci,

146
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,679
and Miss Meng have it.

147
00:12:44,799 --> 00:12:46,399
I don't care if you have it now.

148
00:12:46,519 --> 00:12:48,600
I need it before the bidding starts.

149
00:12:53,279 --> 00:12:54,080
Yuci,

150
00:12:54,639 --> 00:12:55,799
Bai Liangliang wants to get

151
00:12:55,799 --> 00:12:56,960
our project proposal early.

152
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:58,759
I know.

153
00:12:59,799 --> 00:13:01,200
We'll beat her at her own game.

154
00:13:23,399 --> 00:13:25,720
You managed to get out
after I sent you away last time,

155
00:13:27,399 --> 00:13:28,320
But this time,

156
00:13:29,799 --> 00:13:31,200
you won't be as lucky.

157
00:13:37,279 --> 00:13:38,080
Stop!

158
00:13:41,759 --> 00:13:43,519
Rao Yuci, you lied to me!

159
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,000
What are you doing?

160
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:45,720
What am I doing?

161
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:47,320
Let go of me!

162
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:48,279
Calm down.

163
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,279
Let go!

164
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:51,240
Calm down!

165
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:52,919
Just calm down!

166
00:13:53,279 --> 00:13:54,600
Sima Yang, you can head out.

167
00:14:11,679 --> 00:14:13,480
You were my best friend.

168
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:17,960
I shared everything

169
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:19,399
with you.

170
00:14:20,639 --> 00:14:21,879
(Even the warmth of a home.)

171
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:23,480
Mrs. Rao, you should have seen

172
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:24,759
Yuci's defense today.

173
00:14:24,759 --> 00:14:25,879
It was brilliant.

174
00:14:26,879 --> 00:14:28,480
Brilliant, both of you were brilliant.

175
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,840
You are both my daughters.

176
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,240
(Chuxia)
(Our dreams for the company.)

177
00:14:34,759 --> 00:14:35,879
(I held nothing back.)

178
00:14:38,759 --> 00:14:40,759
I never did anything to hurt you.

179
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:45,159
I don't understand why

180
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:49,159
you hate me this much.

181
00:14:49,679 --> 00:14:51,080
I just do.

182
00:14:53,919 --> 00:14:55,360
I hate that everyone thinks

183
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:56,559
you're so kind.

184
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,360
I hate that everyone thinks

185
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,320
everything you have

186
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:00,840
is just your birthright.

187
00:15:01,360 --> 00:15:02,600
You talk about

188
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,960
pursuing fairness in this world,

189
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:06,559
but in reality,

190
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:08,200
you've just been riding

191
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:10,200
the wave of your own privilege.

192
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:12,840
I worked hard too.

193
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:15,320
I'm just as good as you!

194
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:17,440
So why did Professor Han

195
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:18,639
choose you back then

196
00:15:18,639 --> 00:15:20,080
and not me?

197
00:15:23,759 --> 00:15:24,919
The things I have to bleed for

198
00:15:24,919 --> 00:15:26,080
just to obtain,

199
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:27,360
you get without effort.

200
00:15:27,360 --> 00:15:29,279
It just falls into your lap.

201
00:15:29,759 --> 00:15:30,919
How is that fair?

202
00:15:36,279 --> 00:15:37,120
Everyone...

203
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:39,639
Everyone calls you a genius.

204
00:15:40,799 --> 00:15:42,919
You're everyone's treasure.

205
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:45,039
But what about me?

206
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:47,279
I've had to

207
00:15:47,279 --> 00:15:48,919
crawl in your shadow.

208
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:51,480
You even dragged Bai Xia into this.

209
00:15:53,919 --> 00:15:55,240
My own mother.

210
00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:57,080
I didn't even get a chance to know her

211
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:58,399
before she was gone.

212
00:15:58,440 --> 00:16:00,840
And it's all because of you, Rao Yuci.

213
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:03,360
I hate you.

214
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:04,840
Hating you

215
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:06,240
is all I can think of!

216
00:16:08,879 --> 00:16:10,960
Bai Liangliang, you're twisted.

217
00:16:14,320 --> 00:16:15,919
And honestly, you're pathetic.

218
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:18,279
But your life

219
00:16:18,279 --> 00:16:19,840
didn't have to be like this.

220
00:16:20,919 --> 00:16:22,480
Neither of our lives

221
00:16:25,200 --> 00:16:26,519
had to end up this way.

222
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:29,200
I've prepared

223
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:30,600
a little something for everyone.

224
00:16:30,919 --> 00:16:32,399
I hope you all keep up

225
00:16:32,399 --> 00:16:33,559
the hard work.

226
00:16:33,559 --> 00:16:35,000
Thank you, Ms. Bai.

227
00:16:36,240 --> 00:16:37,360
This seat

228
00:16:39,200 --> 00:16:40,840
should have been yours.

229
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:55,120
(Please be safe, Rao Yuci.)

230
00:16:57,039 --> 00:16:58,320
(Please be safe.)

231
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:01,399
Do you regret

232
00:17:01,399 --> 00:17:02,440
the choices you've made?

233
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:04,559
Losing your family.

234
00:17:05,519 --> 00:17:06,559
Losing everything.

235
00:17:07,690 --> 00:17:08,960
You betrayed everyone you loved

236
00:17:08,960 --> 00:17:10,119
just to get what you wanted.

237
00:17:11,359 --> 00:17:13,119
Now, it's time for you to face the law.

238
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:15,200
Do you regret it?

239
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:18,000
I don't regret a single thing.

240
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:23,680
Sima Yang.

241
00:17:24,480 --> 00:17:25,319
Where's Rao Yuci?

242
00:17:25,319 --> 00:17:26,400
She's with Bai Liangliang.

243
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:32,720
Are you okay?

244
00:17:33,039 --> 00:17:34,000
To the hospital, now.

245
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:34,799
I'm fine.

246
00:17:36,039 --> 00:17:37,079
She's fine.

247
00:17:39,039 --> 00:17:40,599
We were all fools.

248
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:41,839
She already had

249
00:17:41,839 --> 00:17:43,400
this whole thing planned.

250
00:17:44,039 --> 00:17:44,960
She doesn't need

251
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:45,960
anyone's help

252
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:47,720
or your protection.

253
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:58,400
Rao Yuci.

254
00:17:59,440 --> 00:18:00,960
Even if I'm gone,

255
00:18:02,519 --> 00:18:03,920
you'll never find peace.

256
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:07,519
Even with me out of the picture,

257
00:18:09,119 --> 00:18:10,599
you'll never be happy.

258
00:18:16,240 --> 00:18:18,960
You two really are a perfect match.

259
00:18:19,240 --> 00:18:20,720
You act like

260
00:18:20,720 --> 00:18:21,920
you're so devoted,

261
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:23,160
but the truth is

262
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:25,079
you're both just living a lie.

263
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:32,680
You'll never be happy together.

264
00:18:50,519 --> 00:18:51,559
What's going on?

265
00:18:51,559 --> 00:18:52,680
It must be something big.

266
00:18:53,100 --> 00:18:54,039
Look! Look over there!

267
00:18:54,039 --> 00:18:55,480
Isn't that Bai Liangliang
from Lysen Group?

268
00:18:55,480 --> 00:18:56,519
This looks terrible.

269
00:18:56,519 --> 00:18:57,440
What did she do?

270
00:18:57,680 --> 00:18:59,079
Why are the police taking her away?

271
00:18:59,079 --> 00:18:59,759
What's the story?

272
00:18:59,759 --> 00:19:00,359
It's just...

273
00:19:25,119 --> 00:19:25,920
Move.

274
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:11,359
What is it, Ren Jing?

275
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:12,680
Mr. Jiang.

276
00:20:13,400 --> 00:20:14,519
Bai Liangliang

277
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:15,890
drugged Rao Yuci at the office

278
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:17,160
and was arrested.

279
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:21,720
What about Rao Yuci?

280
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:23,480
Rao Yuci is fine.

281
00:20:25,599 --> 00:20:26,680
Okay. I understand.

282
00:20:40,680 --> 00:20:41,480
Yes.

283
00:20:42,720 --> 00:20:43,680
I understand.

284
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:45,680
Dongchao,

285
00:20:46,079 --> 00:20:47,640
the financing conference

286
00:20:47,960 --> 00:20:49,359
will proceed as planned.

287
00:21:01,620 --> 00:21:03,260
(Workplace Compensation Agreement)

288
00:21:03,260 --> 00:21:07,940
(Deaf couple killed
in old city factory fire)

289
00:21:11,580 --> 00:21:15,180
(Responsible Party: Rao Shusheng
Family of Party B: Chen Mo)

290
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:23,200
The deaf couple in the newspaper

291
00:21:26,400 --> 00:21:27,480
were your parents?

292
00:21:33,119 --> 00:21:35,279
When the fire broke out
at Rao Shusheng's factory...

293
00:21:40,599 --> 00:21:41,759
They passed away.

294
00:21:41,759 --> 00:21:44,500
(Deaf couple killed in factory fire.
Compensation sparks controversy)

295
00:21:49,980 --> 00:21:53,260
(Twelve years ago)

296
00:22:37,240 --> 00:22:38,359
Can you hurry it up?

297
00:22:39,039 --> 00:22:39,920
Hold the umbrella.

298
00:22:40,799 --> 00:22:42,200
This child, honestly...

299
00:22:50,440 --> 00:22:51,240
Mom,

300
00:22:51,599 --> 00:22:53,319
who is that girl?

301
00:22:53,880 --> 00:22:55,599
The factory manager's daughter.

302
00:22:55,599 --> 00:22:57,200
She's two years older than you.

303
00:22:57,200 --> 00:22:59,640
She's a quiet little girl.

304
00:23:00,640 --> 00:23:02,319
Her dad just lost his temper with her.

305
00:23:02,319 --> 00:23:04,039
It's none of our business,

306
00:23:04,279 --> 00:23:06,319
so don't go asking around.

307
00:23:06,319 --> 00:23:07,359
Now, eat.

308
00:23:19,700 --> 00:23:23,380
(Happy Birthday, Mom)

309
00:23:49,599 --> 00:23:50,400
Hello?

310
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:52,839
Shusheng, where are you?

311
00:23:52,920 --> 00:23:53,920
Get home, quickly.

312
00:23:54,240 --> 00:23:55,240
What's the matter?

313
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:57,559
The voltage here is acting up.

314
00:23:57,559 --> 00:23:59,079
I'm just fixing the wiring.

315
00:23:59,720 --> 00:24:01,079
You need to come back.

316
00:24:01,519 --> 00:24:03,119
It's incredible news.

317
00:24:03,519 --> 00:24:05,200
Yuci has a surprise for you.

318
00:24:05,720 --> 00:24:06,960
(Vehicle Registration Certificate)
A surprise from her?

319
00:24:07,359 --> 00:24:09,279
I'm content with her
not being a troublemaker.

320
00:24:09,599 --> 00:24:11,279
Yuci told me to keep it a secret,

321
00:24:11,279 --> 00:24:13,200
but she opened a stock trading account.

322
00:24:13,680 --> 00:24:15,640
She made some money on the market.

323
00:24:16,119 --> 00:24:17,519
And since she knows you love cars,

324
00:24:17,640 --> 00:24:19,319
she bought you a brand new one.

325
00:24:19,440 --> 00:24:20,359
Hurry back.

326
00:24:22,279 --> 00:24:23,839
Fine. I'm on my way.

327
00:25:03,839 --> 00:25:04,680
Two workers

328
00:25:04,680 --> 00:25:05,720
are trapped inside!

329
00:25:05,720 --> 00:25:06,680
Get them out!

330
00:25:24,380 --> 00:25:27,500
(Workplace Compensation Agreement
Operations Manager: Rao Shusheng)

331
00:25:48,119 --> 00:25:48,920
Hey, kid.

332
00:25:49,279 --> 00:25:51,039
Why don't you have an umbrella?

333
00:25:51,799 --> 00:25:52,920
It's pouring out here,

334
00:25:52,920 --> 00:25:54,079
and it's already dark.

335
00:25:54,279 --> 00:25:55,279
You should head home.

336
00:25:57,519 --> 00:25:58,640
Here, take mine.

337
00:26:00,559 --> 00:26:01,640
Go on, take it.

338
00:26:04,079 --> 00:26:05,279
I said take it.

339
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:06,240
Be a good girl.

340
00:26:11,079 --> 00:26:12,079
Hurry home now.

341
00:26:12,400 --> 00:26:13,200
Listen to me.

342
00:26:48,060 --> 00:26:50,460
(Xinkang Treatment Center,
Duty Room)

343
00:26:50,460 --> 00:26:52,940
(Patient Medical Records,
Name: Rao Yuci)

344
00:27:12,119 --> 00:27:13,160
Hurry home now.

345
00:27:13,480 --> 00:27:14,279
Listen to me.

346
00:27:39,839 --> 00:27:40,559
No! Wait, wait!

347
00:27:40,559 --> 00:27:41,640
Don't hit me! Stop!

348
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:43,200
Why are you following me?

349
00:27:46,759 --> 00:27:48,599
I'm Chen Mo, a psychologist.

350
00:27:54,039 --> 00:27:54,839
Rao Yuci.

351
00:27:57,480 --> 00:27:59,690
Rao Yuci, can you just
let me finish what I have to say?

352
00:28:03,240 --> 00:28:04,039
Rao Yuci,

353
00:28:04,720 --> 00:28:06,119
I kept quiet for our sake.

354
00:28:09,519 --> 00:28:11,000
What's the point of the truth?

355
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:13,160
What would it

356
00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:13,960
actually change?

357
00:28:23,720 --> 00:28:24,759
Do you know how long

358
00:28:24,759 --> 00:28:25,960
it took me to let this go?

359
00:28:26,720 --> 00:28:28,400
Who was I supposed
to tell about my pain?

360
00:28:35,640 --> 00:28:36,359
You get to go home

361
00:28:36,359 --> 00:28:37,680
and have dinner with your parents.

362
00:28:39,839 --> 00:28:40,640
But what about me?

363
00:28:42,440 --> 00:28:43,850
I want to have dinner with them too.

364
00:28:45,519 --> 00:28:46,359
I'd give anything

365
00:28:46,359 --> 00:28:47,519
to have dinner with them.

366
00:28:55,160 --> 00:28:56,440
Listen closely, Rao Yuci.

367
00:28:58,519 --> 00:28:59,759
I've stood on that line between

368
00:28:59,759 --> 00:29:00,559
good and evil.

369
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:05,519
But I don't want to

370
00:29:05,519 --> 00:29:06,759
lose the ability to love.

371
00:29:07,599 --> 00:29:09,039
So I fought so hard

372
00:29:09,039 --> 00:29:10,440
to be someone dependable.

373
00:29:12,519 --> 00:29:13,279
But you don't think

374
00:29:13,279 --> 00:29:14,200
I understand anything.

375
00:29:15,359 --> 00:29:16,640
You never once bothered to ask me

376
00:29:16,640 --> 00:29:18,000
if I was actually hurting.

377
00:29:19,599 --> 00:29:20,720
But I'm human too.

378
00:29:21,720 --> 00:29:22,599
I feel wronged.

379
00:29:22,599 --> 00:29:24,079
I have emotions.

380
00:29:29,079 --> 00:29:30,799
Now, I want to think for myself.

381
00:29:32,519 --> 00:29:33,359
I don't want to die

382
00:29:33,359 --> 00:29:34,640
in this emotional dead end.

383
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:36,599
I want to do everything I can

384
00:29:36,599 --> 00:29:38,000
to protect all that I still have.

385
00:29:43,240 --> 00:29:44,200
I couldn't let go

386
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:45,119
of my parents.

387
00:29:49,279 --> 00:29:50,920
Now, I can't let go of you.

388
00:29:52,559 --> 00:29:53,359
Rao Yuci.

389
00:29:56,119 --> 00:29:57,279
I want to protect you.

390
00:29:59,119 --> 00:29:59,880
When will you stop

391
00:29:59,880 --> 00:30:01,359
pushing me away?

392
00:30:07,279 --> 00:30:08,440
You know me so well.

393
00:30:10,039 --> 00:30:11,599
But I barely know you at all.

394
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:14,240
You're right.

395
00:30:15,240 --> 00:30:16,880
I am a selfish person.

396
00:30:18,079 --> 00:30:19,640
I never considered your feelings.

397
00:30:19,680 --> 00:30:20,519
I never cared

398
00:30:20,519 --> 00:30:21,559
what was on your mind.

399
00:30:24,920 --> 00:30:26,279
But since the day we met,

400
00:30:26,279 --> 00:30:27,759
that's just how we've been.

401
00:30:29,519 --> 00:30:30,920
I've always lived in the dark.

402
00:30:32,960 --> 00:30:34,559
Now that you've found the light,

403
00:30:35,920 --> 00:30:37,359
stay there.

404
00:30:39,640 --> 00:30:41,079
I don't need your protection.

405
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:45,640
This ends here.

406
00:31:07,660 --> 00:31:13,580
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

407
00:31:15,500 --> 00:31:21,580
♪Up to fill my mind
with doubts and pain♪

408
00:31:23,580 --> 00:31:28,940
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

409
00:31:28,940 --> 00:31:31,380
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

410
00:31:31,380 --> 00:31:38,220
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

411
00:31:39,460 --> 00:31:45,380
♪In this dismal dream
where I've been trapped♪

412
00:31:47,540 --> 00:31:54,020
♪you fabricated all these twisted lies♪

413
00:31:55,980 --> 00:31:58,980
♪You could pray, but won't be saved♪

414
00:31:58,980 --> 00:32:03,380
♪Cuz your soul is walking down
a path of destruction♪

415
00:32:08,240 --> 00:32:09,359
(But I'm human too.)

416
00:32:10,359 --> 00:32:11,279
(I feel wronged.)

417
00:32:11,279 --> 00:32:12,720
(I have emotions.)

418
00:32:14,440 --> 00:32:15,240
(Rao Yuci.)

419
00:32:15,759 --> 00:32:16,960
(I want to protect you.)

420
00:32:18,119 --> 00:32:18,880
(When will you stop)

421
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:20,039
(pushing me away?)

422
00:32:20,039 --> 00:32:23,540
♪I'm coming back survived♪

423
00:32:23,540 --> 00:32:27,380
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

424
00:32:27,380 --> 00:32:31,580
♪I'm taking back what' s mine♪

425
00:32:31,580 --> 00:32:36,060
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

426
00:32:36,060 --> 00:32:40,100
♪Lay it to waste♪

427
00:32:40,100 --> 00:32:43,700
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

428
00:32:56,660 --> 00:33:00,420
=Episode 28=
(Fury)

429
00:33:00,941 --> 00:33:03,381
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

430
00:33:03,381 --> 00:33:09,581
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

431
00:33:10,341 --> 00:33:13,541
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

432
00:33:13,541 --> 00:33:18,061
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

433
00:33:18,061 --> 00:33:25,581
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

434
00:33:25,581 --> 00:33:29,501
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

435
00:33:29,501 --> 00:33:33,541
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

436
00:33:33,541 --> 00:33:37,061
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

437
00:33:37,061 --> 00:33:41,021
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

438
00:33:41,021 --> 00:33:45,181
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

439
00:33:45,181 --> 00:33:49,381
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

440
00:33:49,381 --> 00:33:53,181
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

441
00:33:53,181 --> 00:33:57,261
♪Keep walking through the light♪

442
00:33:57,261 --> 00:34:01,461
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

443
00:34:01,461 --> 00:34:07,781
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

444
00:34:24,901 --> 00:34:31,541
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

445
00:34:31,541 --> 00:34:35,381
♪An apology that came too late♪

446
00:34:35,381 --> 00:34:40,021
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

447
00:34:40,101 --> 00:34:47,501
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

448
00:34:47,501 --> 00:34:51,581
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

449
00:34:51,581 --> 00:34:55,661
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

450
00:34:55,661 --> 00:34:59,661
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

451
00:34:59,661 --> 00:35:03,421
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

452
00:35:03,421 --> 00:35:07,621
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

453
00:35:07,621 --> 00:35:11,781
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

454
00:35:11,781 --> 00:35:15,501
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

455
00:35:15,501 --> 00:35:19,541
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

456
00:35:19,541 --> 00:35:23,581
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

457
00:35:23,581 --> 00:35:29,781
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
